{"tid":1047301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社：康明凱竊取華機密","createTime":"2019-03-05T00:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T02:06:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa02e536ed90067987a73f0c3c93ba7c971ff79","tid":1047301,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T00:44:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190305/20626093\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F20626093&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=676a7f68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190305%2F20626093&h=7702dae2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190305/20626093</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新華社：康明凱竊取華機密<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190305/large/chris91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190305%2Flarge%2Fchris91.jpg&h=a4d1a176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n孟晚舟案有新進展之際，內地官媒昨發放去年底在中國被扣押的加拿大前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig，圖）和商人斯帕沃（Spavor Michael）的案情，指康明凱自2017年起竊取、刺探中國情報，斯帕沃則為他提供情報。<br />\n<br />\n孟在加被捕後，中國以危害國家安全為由拘捕康明凱和斯帕沃。新華社昨引述「有關部門」報道，康明凱竊取、刺探國家秘密和情報案調查工作已取得重要進展。康明凱自2017年以來，經常持普通護照和商務簽證入境，通過中國境內的關係人，為境外竊取、刺探國家秘密和情報，有關行為嚴重觸犯中國法律。斯帕沃則向康明凱提供情報。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：談判入直路　傳習月底訪美<br />\n<br />\n處理案件被斥「雙重標準」<br />\n<br />\n有關部門又強調，中國充份保障兩人的合法權利，依法安排領事探視等事宜；將適時啟動下一步司法程序。<br />\n<br />\n有記者在昨天中國外交部記者會上，問到孟晚舟起訴加方侵犯她的憲法權利，另一方面中方不允許康明凱和斯帕沃會見律師，質疑是「雙重標準」。發言人陸慷未正面回應，稱中方嚴格履行《中加領事協定》義務，在處理這類涉及國安的案件做法上，與其他國家沒甚麼不同。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日頭條  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n談判入直路　傳習月底訪美<br />\n<br />\n談判入直路　傳習月底訪美<br />\n孟晚舟打拉布戰　控加國非法扣留報讀當地大學　準備漫長聆訊"},{"pid":"d682c43d251e1e7bec9f894452088df6fa1b9869","tid":1047301,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"有咩機密又講唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25bd2a0db3040b0ec5eb7f233f5d22a40b339cf3","tid":1047301,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d682c43d251e1e7bec9f894452088df6fa1b9869","tid":1047301,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"有咩機密又講唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"民主自由人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684f8b9a158851fb707b924bf9c66ff22920ceb7","tid":1047301,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:03:42.000Z","msg":"拉晒所有加拿大人啦"},{"pid":"9edb85fab274941f3414881295331791eb111fbf","tid":1047301,"uid":33645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T02:06:41.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑, 人地唔發表野佢又唔發表. <br />\n係咪當全世界唔諗野."}]}